channel.title: Cant get Eclipse working?
channel.description:
Hello, i just started using eclipse to code, and i put my server files and client files into it.
My Client launches perfectly fine. But when i try to run my server, it gives me this error: [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.Error: Unresolved compilation problems: IoAcceptor cannot be resolved to a type SocketAcceptor cannot be resolved to a type SocketAcceptorConfig cannot be resolved to a type SocketAcceptorConfig cannot be resolved to a type IoAcceptor cannot be resolved to a type PlayerHandler cannot be resolved to a type Player cannot be resolved to a type PlayerHandler cannot be resolved to a variable PlayerSave cannot be resolved Client cannot be resolved to a type Player cannot be resolved to a type PlayerHandler cannot be resolved to a variable PlayerSave cannot be resolved Client cannot be resolved to a type IoAcceptor cannot be resolved to a type
at server.Server.main(Server.java:129) [/code]
But it runs fine outside of eclipse? Any help?
